Version:
QV SDK    - 2.32.20.28
ixl       - 2.1.0-k
-----------


This problem does not occur when all VFs are in passthrough mode (and the host does not use ixl1):
example: /etc/iov/ixl1.conf
---------
PF {
	  device : "ixl1";
	  num_vfs : 4;
}

DEFAULT {
	  passthrough :	true;
}
---------

